Zomato is a food dilvery company.
Zomato is a leading restaurant search and discovery platform founded in 2008 in India.
Deepinder Goyal and Pankaj Chaddah the co-founder of Zomato.
Zomato provides information, menus and user-reviews of restaurants as well as food delivery options from partner restaurants in more than 1,000 Indian cities and towns.
Asides from food delivery, Zomato offers a wide range of services, including online ordering, table reservations, and reviews of restaurants.
